BEGIN
 I n i t i a l i z e system components
 S t a r t Arduino module and s e n s o r s
 WHILE ( System i s A c t i v e )
 IF ( Methane D e t e c t e d ) THEN
 I g n i t e FireChamber
 Heat B o i l e r
 G e n e r a t e Steam
 A c t i v a t e Dynamo and TEG
 Convert Steam t o E l e c t r i c i t y
 S t o r e Power i n B a t t e r y
 ELSE
 D i s p l a y ”No methane d e t e c t e d , system on s t a n d b y ”
 ENDIF
 Monitor S e n s o r s
